{"tid":627839,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1998年　美元加息升值　熱錢抽離香港　樓價大跌　樓市崩潰　無關供應","createTime":"2018-04-13T10:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T09:02:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d671041d6364015674da7f5cd76b477ca9eff81","tid":627839,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://luan-invest.blogspot.hk/2015/04/2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fluan-invest.blogspot.hk%2F2015%2F04%2F2.html&d=p%2Bzc4n3KPeztpfCSxg%2BGsqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=11261dac\" target=\"_blank\">http://luan-invest.blogspot.hk/2015/04/2.html</a><br />\n<br />\n一種講法，美元上升，香港樓價會跌，現在美元正在上升週期，香港樓價會否下跌？看圖二，兩者又的確有點關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-LmRqWs5O6dw/VRyxfSwwxaI/AAAAAAAACOA/e1t8li28NUw/s1600/Hong%2BKong%2BProperty%2BPrice%2Band%2BUS%2Bdollar%2Brising%2Btrend.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LmRqWs5O6dw%2FVRyxfSwwxaI%2FAAAAAAAACOA%2Fe1t8li28NUw%2Fs1600%2FHong%252BKong%252BProperty%252BPrice%252Band%252BUS%252Bdollar%252Brising%252Btrend.jpg&h=71012260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美元上升對香港樓價的影響只是表象，實質上，美元上升影響熱錢流向才是真正原因，而左右熱錢的流向，是國際市場拆借美元的利率即倫敦同業拆息(LIBOR)和香港同業拆息(HIBOR)之間的差距(spread)。<br />\n<br />\n由於聯系匯率，港元與美元掛鈎，理論上HIBOR的趨勢必須跟隨LIBOR，在一般情下HIBOR與LIBOR的走勢一致，基本上差距很窄(見圖三)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-86v0nN9xrGg/VRyz42_78BI/AAAAAAAACOw/ZpjvWiK8LaQ/s1600/3-month%2BLibor%2Band%2B3-month%2Bhibor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-86v0nN9xrGg%2FVRyz42_78BI%2FAAAAAAAACOw%2FZpjvWiK8LaQ%2Fs1600%2F3-month%252BLibor%252Band%252B3-month%252Bhibor.jpg&h=245db5ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從過往經驗，當HIBOR高於LIBOR(圖四)，利率差距出現正數，例如97年亞洲金融風 暴，HIBOR大幅高於LIBOR擊退炒家，便令資金流走。然而由於港元跟人民幣趨向强勢，因此HIBOR低於LIBOR，利率差距出現負數引發資金流 入，銀根充裕推動借貸，從而推升資產價格。2008年全球金融海嘯的時侯，資金流向美元避險令正利率差距再次短暫地出現，引發資金短暫地流出，銀根短暫地 收緊引發地產價格短暫下跌，2009年之後美國量化寬鬆，但人民幣仍然强勢，令HIBOR又再低於LIBOR，負利率差距持續，在港熱錢充裕，銀行水浸而 推動借貸是香港地產價格上升的其中很大原因。"},{"pid":"fae0b9624855226cab99b2e37460e59d8835a7c4","tid":627839,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T20:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecca2922e2e7e65d89ff50f86e952bf0973a1a8","tid":627839,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:42:27.000Z","msg":"香港今次冇乜錢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78e6fa990439c8075f02b3494e8a024ac3b1151","tid":627839,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T23:05:54.000Z","msg":"經濟白痴一問點解H按低會多錢流入"},{"pid":"8bc4ec8132da5c262c9616c70b0cab560cf89f09","tid":627839,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78e6fa990439c8075f02b3494e8a024ac3b1151","tid":627839,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T23:05:54.000Z","msg":"經濟白痴一問點解H按低會多錢流入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"呢篇文章講銀行自己點賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.centanet.com/home/ColumnArticle.aspx?id=8739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.centanet.com%2Fhome%2FColumnArticle.aspx%3Fid%3D8739&d=p%2Bzc4n3KPeztpfCSxg%2BGsqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=b5f6c7e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.centanet.com/home/ColumnArticle.aspx?id=8739</a><br />\n<br />\n主要係　銀行透過借錢俾人　向債仔收息去賺錢<br />\n咁銀行邊度o黎錢借俾人？　一個方法就係銀行向其他有錢銀行借錢<br />\n既然銀行自己都要借　自然銀行自己都要還利息　呢個利息o既息率就係HIBOR<br />\nHIBOR高　自然銀行要向客仔收返高ｄ息率先賺到錢<br />\n<br />\n熱錢就係跨國炒賣活動o既資金<br />\n炒家炒o野係會借錢去炒　唔係全部自己出　咁就可以有咁大炒咁大<br />\n<br />\nHIBOR低　＝＞　銀行貸款息率低　＝＞　吸引熱錢去果度炒o野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望我冇講錯啦"},{"pid":"9a04fb26d1566c07b7037db11dffe1c2f890ace0","tid":627839,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ecca2922e2e7e65d89ff50f86e952bf0973a1a8","tid":627839,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:42:27.000Z","msg":"香港今次冇乜錢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"無錢走就唔會港元跌啦"},{"pid":"bc7b5e344c3f85748d04099391b5534282579129","tid":627839,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ecca2922e2e7e65d89ff50f86e952bf0973a1a8","tid":627839,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:42:27.000Z","msg":"香港今次冇乜錢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"大陸擺左咁多錢在香港銀行"}]}